    "description": "<strong>Welcome to Mini Mart!</strong> A mini sized shop and town sim.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/816392fa7aa71118f9dcad0ada54e56c.avif?t=1656517584\" width=618 height=170 /></span><br><br>Beginning with a rundown store and no money in the bank, a new burst of motivation stirs you to make something of yourself and your business.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/0f021af880978fd3b71e534427fff661.poster.avif?t=1656517584\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/0f021af880978fd3b71e534427fff661.webm?t=1656517584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/0f021af880978fd3b71e534427fff661.mp4?t=1656517584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What you'll be doing in mini mart:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In your store</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keep your store tidy and your shelves stocked with merchandise.<br></li><li>Tear down broken shelves and build new ones where you'd like.<br></li><li>Upgrade and customize your shop size, look, and efficiency.<br></li><li>Hire employees to automate shop tasks.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/d855bf1553b02a8ee6fab4eda9786db1.webp?t=1656517584\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/d855bf1553b02a8ee6fab4eda9786db1.poster.avif?t=1656517584\" class=\"bb_img\" width=618 height=112 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About town</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The morning, day and night cycle gives you the freedom to choose how to spend your time.<br></li><li>Build relationships with townsfolk to unlock new merch, store upgrades, and staff.<br></li><li>Do activities to level up speed, strength and social stats.<br></li><li>Cook food, watch tv, or read a book at home.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841960/extras/ca38bd85be54acddb0789fa5f7c9144a.avif?t=1656517584\" width=618 height=170 /></span>",
